{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, we can see that the gap between different datasets varies.",
    "On TriviaQA, the performance gap between ChatGPT and Llama2-13B-Chat enhanced with RAG is relatively small.",
    "However, on more challenging QA datasets NQ and PopQA, the gaps are substantial.",
    "This is because these datasets involve more updated and long-tail knowledge, making it challenging to rely solely on LLM's inherent knowledge.",
    "By effectively augmenting with external information, our method provides greater benefits on such knowledge-intensive datasets, enabling substantial capability enhancement beyond what can be achieved through scaling model parameters alone."
  ]
}